                            "description": "Total inverse lifetime inverse_tau = k_1 + k_2 vs the pathway-1 rate constant k_1 (linear axes). A straight line of slope 1 and intercept k_2 = 2.0e-6 s⁻¹ — the signature of additive parallel first-order removal rates (S&P Eq. 2.8).",
                            "x": {"variable": "k_1", "label": "Pathway-1 rate constant k_1 (s⁻¹)"},
                            "y": {"variable": "inverse_tau", "label": "Total inverse lifetime inverse_tau (s⁻¹)"}
